  "summary": {
    "as": "Public Law",
    "asOf": "2021-11-10",
    "date": "2021-11-16T15:17:19Z",
    "text": "Ensuring Compliance Against Drug Diversion Act of 2021\n\nThis bill provides statutory authority for certain regulations governing the modification, transfer, and termination of a registration to manufacture, distribute, or dispense controlled substances.\n\n It terminates the registration of individuals and entities when they die, cease legal existence, discontinue business, or surrender such registration. It sets forth notification requirements, as well as conditions for transferring or assigning a registration."
